Eater LA highlights a variety of standout pizza spots across Orange County, focusing
on places known for quality ingredients, wood-fired ovens, and consistent execution.
Several restaurants are repeatedly praised for their crust texture, 
balanced sauces, and creative toppings. Among the notable spots mentioned are Fuoco Pizzeria Napolentana 
in Fullerton, Sgt. Pepperoni's Pizza store in Newport Beach, Square Pie Guys for 
Detroit style slices, and Folks Pizzeria in Costa Mesa.  The list includes both 
casual slice shops and more upscale artisan pizzerias, reflecting the diversity 
pizza scene.  Overall, Eater LA emphasizes craftsmanship, regional styles, and 
local followings when identifying the best pizza in the area.